sequenceDiagram
  participant Frontend
  participant API
  participant UseCase
  participant Repository
  participant DB
  Frontend->>API: Request with bearer token
  API->>API: Verify JWT and extract user_id, tenant_id
  alt Access token expired
    API-->>Frontend: 401 Unauthorized
    Frontend->>API: POST /auth/refresh with refresh token
    API->>API: Verify refresh token
    API-->>Frontend: New access token and refresh token
    Frontend->>API: Retry original request with new bearer token
  end
  opt GET or PUT /me
    API->>DB: Read user profile by user_id
  end
  API->>UseCase: Execute with tenant_id
  UseCase->>Repository: Tenant-scoped operation
  Repository->>DB: SQL where tenant_id = $1
  DB-->>Frontend: Tenant data only
